OL,3,CFour arrested after death in seaside
OL,4,Ctown
OL,6,FPolice in Whitby are investigating the
OL,7,Fdeath of a man in his late 40s from
OL,8,FHalifax.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,11,Fdisturbance at an address on
OL,12,FFlowergate shortly after 11pm on
OL,13,FSunday 15 March and found the man
OL,14,Funresponsive.
OL,16,FCPR was given to the man by medics at
OL,17,Fthe scene but he could not be revived.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
