OL,3,CFour arrested after death in seaside
OL,4,Ctown
OL,6,FFour men have since been arrested as
OL,7,Fpart of a manslaughter investigation
OL,8,Fand witnesses are being asked to come
OL,9,Fforward.
OL,11,FThe man's family are supported by
OL,12,Fspecially trained officers. North
OL,13,FYorkshire Police said: "This
OL,14,Finvestigation remains ongoing and
OL,15,Fthere is a significant police presence
OL,16,Fin the area to support the community.
OL,18,F"Detectives have already spoken to a
OL,19,Fnumber of witnesses but are urging
OL,20,Fanyone with information who has yet to
OL,21,Fspeak to them to get in touch."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
